traits.description: Increase final damage by **12%**. The Wanderer's base physical ATK is increased to the highest value out of their physical/flame/frost/volt base ATK. When the main slot weapon is Onyx Tortoise, normal attack damage is increased by **30%**.

Increase final damage by **15%**. The Wanderer's base physical ATK is increased to the highest value out of their physical/flame/frost/volt base ATK. When the main slot weapon is Onyx Tortoise, normal attack damage is increased by **50%**.
